Zote mbili ni vipengele vya JavaScript 1.7. Cha kwanza ni viambajengo vya kiwango cha kizuizi:

  ```let``` hukuruhusu kutangaza viambajengo, ikizuia upeo wake kwa kizuizi, taarifa, au usemi ambao inatumiwa. Hii ni tofauti na neno muhimu la ```var```, ambalo hufafanua kiambajengo kimataifa, au ndani ya eneo la kazi nzima bila kujali upeo wa kizuizi.

Cha pili kinaitwa ubomoaji:

  Ugavi wa ubomoaji unawezesha kutoa data kutoka kwa safu au vitu kwa kutumia sintaksia ambayo inaakisi ujenzi wa safu na maandishi ya kitu.
  ...
  Jambo moja muhimu sana unaloweza kufanya na ugavi wa ubomoaji ni kusoma muundo mzima katika taarifa moja, ingawa kuna mambo kadhaa ya kupendeza unayoweza kufanya nayo, kama inavyoonyeshwa katika sehemu iliyojaa mifano inayofuata.

Kwa wale wanaojua Python, inafanana na sintaksia hii:
```>>> a, (b, c) = (1, (2, 3))
>>> a, b, c
(1, 2, 3)
```
Sehemu ya kwanza ya msimbo ni fupi kwa:
```var {Hotkey: Hotkey} = require("sdk/hotkeys");
// Au
var Hotkey = require("sdk/hotkeys").Hotkey;
```
Unaweza kuandika tena sehemu ya pili ya msimbo kama:
```let Cc = Components.classes;
let Ci = Components.interfaces;
let Cr = Components.results;
let Cu = Components.utils;
```

Kwa kuwa ufuatiliaji haufanyi kazi kwa ujumla (isipokuwa tu kama mpangilio wa sifa unaendana: ```JSON.stringify({a:1,b:2}) !== JSON.stringify({b:2,a:1})```) lazima uangalie hesabu ya sifa na ulinganishe kila sifa pia:

```const objectsEqual = (o1, o2) =>
    Object.keys(o1).length === Object.keys(o2).length
        && Object.keys(o1).every(p => o1[p] === o2[p]);
const obj1 = { name: 'John', age: 33};
const obj2 = { age: 33, name: 'John' };
const obj3 = { name: 'John', age: 45 };
console.log(objectsEqual(obj1, obj2)); // kweli
console.log(objectsEqual(obj1, obj3)); // sio kweli```

Ikiwa unahitaji ulinganisho wa kina, unaweza kuita kitendakazi kwa kujirudia:

```const obj1 = { name: 'John', age: 33, info: { married: true, hobbies: ['sport', 'art'] } };
const obj2 = { age: 33, name: 'John', info: { hobbies: ['sport', 'art'], married: true } };
const obj3 = { name: 'John', age: 33 };
const objectsEqual = (o1, o2) =>
    typeof o1 === 'object' && Object.keys(o1).length > 0
        ? Object.keys(o1).length === Object.keys(o2).length
            && Object.keys(o1).every(p => objectsEqual(o1[p], o2[p]))
        : o1 === o2;
console.log(objectsEqual(obj1, obj2)); // kweli
console.log(objectsEqual(obj1, obj3)); // sio kweli```

Halafu ni rahisi kutumia kitendakazi hiki kulinganisha vitu katika safu:
```const arr1 = [obj1, obj1];
const arr2 = [obj1, obj2];
const arr3 = [obj1, obj3];
const arraysEqual = (a1, a2) =>
   a1.length === a2.length && a1.every((o, idx) => objectsEqual(o, a2[idx]));
console.log(arraysEqual(arr1, arr2)); // kweli
console.log(arraysEqual(arr1, arr3)); // sio kweli
```

